ation)|Jutra Award for Best Animated Film]]\n|-\n| ''[[A Matter of Loaf and Death|Wallace & Gromit: A Matter of Loaf and Death]]''\n| UK\n| Clay/puppet\n| 29\n| [[Annie Award for Best Animated Short Subject]]<br /> [[BAFTA|BAFTA Award for Best Short Animation]]<br />Nominated - [[Academy Award for Best Animated Short Film]]\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Head over Heels (2012 film)|Head over Heels]]''\n| UK\n| Puppet\n| 10\n| Nominated - [[Academy Award for Best Animated Short Film]]\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|Lettres de femmes|fr}}''\n| France\n| Puppet\n| 12\n| [[AIAFF|AIAFF Short Film Audience Award]]\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Adventures of Malia]]''\n| India\n| Cutout\n| 13\n| Independent short film by a 16 year old.<br />\nColorTape International Film Festival Honorary Mention Award for Best Foreign Film <br />\nGlobal Independent Film Award for Best Under 18 Filmmaker <br />\nAwareness Film Festival - Merit Award of Awareness <br />\nNominated - TOFUZI International Festival of Animation Films Award for Best Children Film<br />\nNominated - Global Independent Film Award for Best Environmental Film<br />\nNominated - Twister Alley International Film Festival Award for Best Family Short<br />\nNominated - Twister Alley International Film Festival Award for Best Animated Short<br />\nNominated - Phoenix Film Festival Melbourne Award for Best Animation<br />\nNominated - Phoenix Film Festival Melbourne Award for Best Student Film<br />\nNominated - Phoenix Film Festival Melbourne Award for Best New Filmmaker<br />\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Stop motion]]\n* [[Clay animation]]\n** [[List of films featuring clay animation]]\n* [[Puppetoon]]\n* [[History of animation]]\n* [[List of highest-grossing animated films#Stop-motion animation|Highest-grossing stop-motion animation films]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Animation}}\n{{Animationfilmlist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:List of stop motion films}}\n[[Category:Stop-motion animated films|*01]]\n[[Category:Lists of animated fi